                           <note>From the third epistle onwards all the epistles (46) are marked as <foreign xml:lang="gez">fǝnnāwe malʾǝkt</foreign>. 
                              In <ref type="mss" corresp="ESdd036"/>, 29 epistles are marked as <foreign xml:lang="gez">fǝnnāwe malʾǝktāt</foreign> as opposed
                              to 20 epistles marked as <foreign xml:lang="gez">malʾǝktāt</foreign>. <ref type="mss" corresp="ESgkm001"/> and <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmakm012"/> contain 28 
                              <foreign xml:lang="gez">fǝnnāwe malʾǝktāt</foreign> as opposed to 22 <foreign xml:lang="gez">malʾǝktāt</foreign>. Despite the difference in naming, the
                              contents of the first 22 epistles in the present manuscript correspond to the first 22 <foreign xml:lang="gez">malʾǝktāt</foreign> in other manuscripts.</note>
                        </msItem>
